<i>noun</i>: 햇빛 [해삗/핻삗], 햇발 [해빨/핻빨], 일광 [일광] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>햇빛 [해삗/핻삗]</dt><br>
<dd>1. sunlight; sunbeam; sunshine</dd><br>
<dd>해의 빛.</dd><br>
<dd>Light from the sun.</dd><br>
<dd>2. seeing the light</dd><br>
<dd>(비유적으로) 세상에 알려져 칭찬받거나 이름을 날리게 되는 것.</dd><br>
<dd>(figurative) A state of becoming known to the public and receiving praise or gaining fame.</dd><br>
<dt>햇발 [해빨/핻빨]</dt><br>
<dd>sunbeam; ray of sunlight</dd><br>
<dd>사방으로 퍼지는 햇살.</dd><br>
<dd>A ray of sunlight radiating in all directions.</dd><br>
<dt>일광 [일광]</dt><br>
<dd>sunlight; sunbeam; sunshine</dd><br>
<dd>해의 빛.</dd><br>
<dd>A light from the sun.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>